{"tid":1211950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衝擊立法會：警員灣仔拔槍截可疑車　檢手襪保鮮紙拘4漢","createTime":"2019-06-12T16:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T08:12:53.000Z","uid":20058,"like":16,"dislike":361,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"4ffa5b7f8c1da64d7ad672de14abe276889ae2eb","tid":1211950,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:57:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/128807942654/posts/10156916407532655?s=100001313257075&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F128807942654%2Fposts%2F10156916407532655%3Fs%3D100001313257075%26sfns%3Dmo&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgvx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=91cf7110\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/128807942654/posts/10156916407532655?s=100001313257075&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n昨午（12日）正當警方施放催淚彈驅散示威者時，警方接報有人用車運送汽油彈到金鐘，遂展開追查及兜截，至下午5時05分，警員在告士打道舊灣仔警署外發現該可疑私家車，即時將其截停，期間警員拔槍戒備，將車上4名年齡由22至25歲男子拖出車外，然後搜查車廂。 <br />\n<br />\n警員在車內檢獲1個口罩、25對勞工手襪、5卷保鮮紙、1個鐵鉗及1個不屬該車的車牌，遂以涉嫌藏有工具可作非法用途將4人拘捕。案件已交由灣仔警區反三合會調查組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190613/mobile/bkn-20190613002859718-0613_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190613%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190613002859718-0613_00822_001.html&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgvx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=dac6c340\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190613/mobile/bkn-20190613002859718-0613_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"20a6551fb3042dc332c0c82174fb48e4431ead5d","tid":1211950,"uid":810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4a12d27252d29321abfadd373fe73b24b4439c","tid":1211950,"uid":14075,"like":338,"dislike":2,"score":336,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:59:01.000Z","msg":"保鮮紙咁危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},